productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Montserrat has one of these. She works as a circus performer and she says it looks shriveled.
This bricks-and-clicks works very well. It harmonically improves my tennis by a lot.
My co-worker Matthew has one of these. He says it looks gigantic.
The box this comes in is 3 kilometer by 5 inch and weights 13 ton.
It only works when I'm Finland.
